{
  "texts": [
    "In such cases, we report the number of annotated samples instead.",
    "To maintain consistency and statistical significance, we have included only datasets with a minimum of ten subjects or samples.",
    "Datasets smaller than this threshold are typically inadequate for model development in practical applications.Regarding annotated emotions, we report the number of distinct classes for categorical emotion models and valence and/or arousal for dimensional models, as discussed in Subsection 1.2.",
    "Some datasets offer both types of annotations.",
    "We acknowledge that certain properties are difficult to evaluate precisely and indicate them with an asterisk (*) symbol."
  ]
}